  <description><![CDATA[<p><span>A warm welcome is provided by the team at the Hotel Sonnschein. The hotel has room types to suit everyone and leisure facilities including two indoor pools.</span></p>
<h2><span>Rooms</span></h2>
<p><span>The hotel has a relaxed and informal atmosphere. </span><span>The main hotel building is the original building, which houses the reception, dining room and some guest bedrooms. Two newer wings are connected to the main building, one is decorated in a traditional Tyrolean style and the other has a more modern style.</span></p>
<p><span>Ideal for families, with a variety of </span><span>room types including spacious family rooms. There is also a great variety of twin and single rooms available.</span></p>
<h2><span>Facilities</span></h2>
<p><span>The Sonnschein</span><span> has</span><span> leisure facilities including a wellness area with two swimming pools, steam room, infrared cabin, and fitness room. There is also a games room with table tennis and pool table, and a children's playroom. </span></p>]]></description>
